Stop Polio. ✋🏾👊🏾👊🏾
 
@MOHKenya together with @UnicefKenya and partners have today launched the #ENDPolio campaign in 9 counties. 
 
Ensure your child is protected from #polio if you are in any of these counties; Busia, Bungoma, Trans-Nzoia, West Pokot and Turkana, Nairobi, Kiambu https://t.co/40U1ImtZgT
